Package: geotuple
Type: Package
Title: Provides Exploratory Geospatial Data Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Roland", "Hansson", email = "rolandhhansson@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A web app, built on the OpenCPU framework, to visualize and perform geospatial analysis on point
  data (gridded), thematically organized in a PostGIS (PostgreSQL) database at multiple resolutions (map scales).
Depends: R (>= 3.2.4)
License: GPL-3
Imports:
  opencpu,
  RPostgreSQL
Suggests: spdep
LazyData: TRUE
URL: http://www.geotuple.org
